    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and roughly chop your<strong> shallot[s]</strong></p><p>Peel and roughly chop your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Cut your <strong>red chilli[es]</strong><span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>in half lengthways, deseed (scrape the seeds out with a teaspoon) and chop finely</p><p>Chop your<strong> lime[s]</strong> in half</p><p>Separate your <strong>coriander leaves </strong>from the <strong>stalks</strong>, then chop both finely</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
